---

<div class="w-full flex flex-col items-center justify-center font-bold">
  <div
    class="max-w-[2400px] flex flex-col items-center justify-center mt-10 md:mt-20 text-white"
  >
    <div
      class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 justify-center items-start gap-4"
    >
      <div class="hidden justify-start items-end md:flex h-full">
        <Image src={img5} alt="Drum Mixer" class="w-[80%]" />
      </div>
      <div 
      class="hidden md:flex-col items-start justify-start pt-4 md:flex">
        <h1 class="md:text-4xl text-2xl text-black text-center w-full">
          Two Year Warranty
        </h1>
        <br />
        <p class="md:text-2xl text-lg text-grisT text-center w-full">
          We stand behind our top-tier quality with the <br />
          highest warranty in the market
        </p>
      </div>
      <div
        class="flex flex-col justify-center items-center md:items-start md:justify-start lg:items-start lg:justify-start gap-4 bg-blueMain md:rounded-t-2xl p-8 md:h-full"
      >
        <div
          id="DrumMixer"
          class="scroll-mt-20 text-2xl md:text-4xl w-full text-center lg:text-start md:text-start"
        >
          <h1 class="text-redBg">TRIASO®</h1>
          <h1 class="">DRUM MIXER</h1>
        </div>
        <p
          class="text-grisSubP text-base md:text-lg text-center lg:text-justify md:text-justify"
        >
          Heavy-duty drum mixers engineered for continuous operation and precise
          asphalt blending. Built with heat-resistant alloy steel and optimized
          air-flow design, they achieve uniform drying, minimal fines loss, and
          maximum fuel efficiency — ensuring long service life and consistent
          performance under demanding conditions
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="w-full bg-blueMain p-6">
      <h1 class="text-xl text-center md:text-start lg:text-start md:text-4xl">
        RANGING FROM 10 TO 500 TPH
      </h1>
    </div>
    <div class="block md:hidden">
      <Image src={img7} alt="Drum Mixer" class="w-1/2" />
      <div class="flex-col flex md:hidden items-start justify-start pt-4">
        <h1 class="md:text-4xl text-2xl text-black text-center w-full">
          Two Year Warranty
        </h1>
        <br />
        <p class="md:text-2xl text-lg text-grisT text-center w-full">
          We stand behind our top-tier quality with the <br />
          highest warranty in the market
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div
    class="w-full flex flex-col items-center justify-center mt-20 text-black max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4"
  >
    <h1 class="text-xl md:text-3xl text-center md:mb-10">
      Asphalt plants for the smallest jobs to large projects
    </h1>
    <a href="/DrumMixers" class="text-lg md:text-2xl text-center text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-700 underline">
      Discover all asphalt plants ranges and models >
    </a>
    <div class="relative overflow-hidden bg-black transform-gpu">
      <video
        src={Video1}
        autoplay
        muted
        loop
        playsinline
        class="block w-full h-auto object-cover transform-gpu will-change-transform [backface-visibility:hidden] bg-black"
      ></video>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="w-full bg-[#2e2e2e] flex flex-col justify-center items-center">
    <Image src={logo} alt="Triaso Logo" class="w-[500px] lg:w-full md:w-full" /><br />
    <div
      class="w-full bg-[url(/HeroS.webp)] bg-cover bg-no-repeat bg-center max-h-[900px] lg:min-h-[900px] md:min-h-[900px] flex justify-center items-center"
    >
      <div class="flex flex-col mx-auto max-w-7xl px-8">
        <h1
          class="text-white text-2xl lg:text-4xl font-bold text-center lg:text-start md:text-start"
        >
          Fully Portable
        </h1>
        <br />
        <p
          class="text-base text-center lg:text-justify md:text-justify lg:text-lg text-white font-thin"
        >
          All components of our asphalt plants are engineered for complete
          transportability, allowing for efficient and quick setup. Their robust
          structure enables a smooth, hassle-free installation directly on-site.
        </p><br />
        <p
          class="text-base text-center lg:text-justify md:text-justify lg:text-lg text-white font-thin"
        >
          We design our equipment with an integrated fifth wheel, eliminating
          the need for a low-boy or a flatbed trailer during transport.
        </p>
        <p
          class="text-base text-center lg:text-justify md:text-justify lg:text-lg text-white font-thin pb-5"
        >
          The complete asphalt plant can be transported in only three trailer
          loads, simplifying logistics and reducing setup time.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="relative overflow-hidden max-w-7xl mx-auto transform-gpu">
    <video
      src={Video2}
      autoplay
      muted
      loop
      playsinline
      class="block w-full h-auto object-cover transform-gpu will-change-transform [backface-visibility:hidden] bg-black"
    ></video>
  </div>
  <div class="relative overflow-hidden max-w-7xl mx-auto transform-gpu">
    <video
      src={Video3}
      autoplay
      muted
      loop
      playsinline
      class="block w-full h-auto object-cover transform-gpu will-change-transform [backface-visibility:hidden] bg-black"
    ></video>
  </div>

  <div
    class="max-w-7xl my-10 mx-5 lg:mx-auto md:mx-auto p-4 flex flex-col items-center justify-center bg-white rounded-2xl"
  >
    <h2 class="text-xl text-center lg:text-2xl md:text-3xl">
      Retractable Drag Slat for Efficient Transport and Operation
    </h2>
    <div class="">
      <div class="w-full flex justify-center">
        <video src={Video4} autoplay muted playsinline class="w-full md:w-3/5"></video>
      </div>
      <p
        class="text-black text-center lg:text-justify md:text-justify font-semibold mt-5 mb-5"
      >
        The vertical drag slat features a retractable configuration that
        complies with DOT transportation height limits, ensuring safe and legal
        road transport. Once the drum mixer is installed on-site, the elevator
        extends to its full operational height, allowing efficient material
        discharge into truck with minimal setup time. This smart design improves
        logistics while maintaining high performance during loading and
        discharge operations.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="w-full bg-gradient-to-b from-grisT to-bgMain">
    <div
      class="w-full max-w-7xl mx-auto px-8 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 py-10 justify-center items-center"
    >
      <div class="w-full flex justify-center">
        <Image src={rap} alt="Drum Collar" class="w-3/5" />
      </div>
      <div class="w-full text-white">
        <h1
          class="font-bold text-2xl text-center lg:text-start md:text-start lg:text-4xl"
        >
          RAP COLLAR & BIN
        </h1>
        <p
          class="font-thin text-base text-center lg:text-start md:text-start lg:text-lg"
        >
          Our RAP system can incorporate
        </p>
        <h2
          class="font-bold text-lg text-center lg:text-start md:text-start lg:text-2xl"
        >
          up to 50%
        </h2>
        <p class="text-center lg:text-start md:text-start">
          of recycled asphalt pavement
        </p>
        <br />
        <p
          class="font-thin text-base text-center md:text-start lg:text-start lg:text-lg"
        >
          The drum collar is engineered to provide the controlled and efficient
          entry of Recycled Asphalt Pavement (RAP) into the mixing zone. Fed
          directly from the RAP bin via a dedicated conveyor, the material
          enters the drum smoothly and uniformly.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="w-full max-w-7xl mx-auto px-5 text-center">
      <p class="font-thin text-base lg:text-lg">
        For very 10% of RAP, <br />
        the cost of hot-mix production
      </p>
      <h2 class="font-bold text-lg lg:text-2xl">decreases 7%</h2>
      <p class="font-thin text-base lg:text-lg">
        By recycling up to 50% RAP woth our plants,<br />
        you can achieve approximately 35% savings in hot-mix production costs.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="w-full max-w-7xl mx-auto px-8 py-10">
    <h2
      class="text-xl lg:text-3xl text-center md:text-end lg:text-end font-bold"
    >
      RAP ENTRY FLIGHTS
    </h2>
  </div>
  <div
    class="w-full max-w-7xl mx-auto px-8 flex flex-col lg:grid md:grid lg:grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-2 py-10 gap-6 items-center"
  >
    <div class="w-full">
      <h2
        class="text-base text-center lg:text-start md:text-start md:text-lg font-bold"
      >
        DRUM MIX MODIFICATION FOR RAP
      </h2><br />
      <div class="text-justify md:text-start lg:text-start">
        <p class="text-base md:text-lg font-thin">
          RAP is introduced through a collar located at an intermediate point of
          the drum, before the mixing zone. From this point on, the material
          never comes into direct contact with the burner flame.
        </p>
        <p class="text-base font-thin md:text-lg mt-10">
          The dedicated RAP flight are engineered to provide balanced heat
          distribution, smooth material flow, and reduced blue smoke or buildup.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div>
      <Image src={rapEntry} alt="Rap Entry Flights" class="rounded-md" />
    </div>
    <div class="flex col-span-2">
      <div class="space-y-5">
        <h1 class="font-bold text-3xl uppercase">
          Variable-Speed Rotation Drives
        </h1>
        <h2 class="font-bold text-xl uppercase">
          for Drum Rotation Systems for High-RAP Incorporation
        </h2>
        <p class="font-thin">
          Our latest innovation for high-RAP incorporation is the use of
          Variable-Speed Rotation Drives for Drum Rotation Systems. <br />
          According to our investigation and multiple field studies, RAP quality is
          directly affected by its heating exposure time inside the drum, which allows
          the RAP binder to fully blend and incorporate with the virgin aggregates.
        </p>
        <h2>
          This exposure time must be adjusted according to the RAP percentage in
          the mix.
        </h2>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="w-full">
    <div class="w-full flex justify-center">
      <LearnBtnBlue href="/RapRecycled"/>
    </div>
    <Image src={HeroS2} alt="Asphalt plant specializing in the incorporation of RAP" class="w-full" />
  </div>
  <div
    class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 items-center justify-center mt-10 gap-10 max-w-7xl mx-auto"
  >
    <Image src={img8} alt="Rap Bin" class="hidden md:block" />
    <div class="flex flex-col text-grisT items-center justify-center">
      <h1
        class="text-xl lg:text-2xl mb-4 text-center lg:text-start md:text-start w-full"
      >
        RAP BINS
      </h1>
      <p
        class="text-base text-center lg:text-justify md:text-justify px-5 lg:px-0 md:px-0 lg:text-lg font-thin mb-4"
      >
        Triaso® RAP Bins are designed to efficiently handle and transport
        recycled asphalt pavement (RAP) in asphalt plants. Built for durability,
        they ensure a consistent and reliable flow of material, enabling
        seamless integration into your plant's production process. With their
        robust construction, Triaso® RAP Feeders can handle the heavy, abrasive
        nature of RAP, reducing downtime and ensuring high operational
        efficiency.
      </p>
      <Image src={img8} alt="Rap Bin" class="block md:hidden" />
      <LearnBtn href="/BinUnits"/>
    </div>
  </div>
  <ASPanels  />
  
  <div id="ColdMix"></div>
  <div
    class="w-full flex flex-col items-center justify-center mt-5 md:mt-20 max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4"
  >
    <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl text-redBg">
      Hot-mix
      <span class="text-3xl md:text-4xl text-black">Pugmill</span>
    </h1>
    <div>
      <video src={pugmillVideo} autoplay muted></video>
    </div>
    <div
      class="w-full grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 justify-center items-center gap-8 mt-20 mb-8"
    >
      <div class="flex flex-col items-start justify-center gap-4">
        <p
          class="text-base md:text-lg text-grisP text-center lg:text-justify md:text-justify text-[#2b2b2b]"
        >
          The pugmill is a optional component at the final stage of the drum-mix
          process, used whem the hot mix design or project specifications
          require additional blending to meet uniformity requirements. Equipped
          with two heavy-duty shafts and precisely engineered mixing flights, it
          ensures complete homogenization and consistency throughout the
          material.
        </p>
        <Image src={img2} alt="Pugmill component for the drum-mix" class="block md:hidden my-4" />
        <p
          class="text-base md:text-lg text-grisP text-center lg:text-justify md:text-justify text-[#2b2b2b]"
        >
          Built for durability and continuous operation, its robust structure
          and efficient mixing system provide precise control over the final
          blend. Designed for ease of maintenance and reliable performance, the
          Triaso® pugmill delivers long-lasting efficiency even under the most
          demanding production conditions.
        </p>
      </div>
      <Image src={pugmill} alt="Pugmill component for the drum-mix" class="hidden md:block" />
    </div>
    <LearnBtn href="/ColdMix"/>
  </div>

  <HeatingSystem />
  <Baghouses />
  <div
    class="w-full bg-[url(/HeroCabin.webp)] bg-cover bg-no-repeat bg-center my-10 py-20"
  >
    <div class="w-full max-w-7xl mx-auto px-8">
      <div class="w-full">
        <h1
          class="lg:text-4xl text-2xl text-white w-full text-center lg:text-end md:text-end mb-10"
        >
          CONTROL CABIN
        </h1>
        <div class="w-full grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
          <div class="text-white">
            <h2 class="font-bold text-sm md:text-base">
              Walls and roof made of 16-gauge sheet metal with insulated panels.
            </h2>
            <p class="font-thin text-sm md:text-base">
              Provides durability and thermal insulation, ensuring structural
              strength while maintaining a controlled interior environment.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="w-full text-white">
            <p class="text-sm md:text-base font-thin">
              Towable control cabin designed for quick, safe, and practical
              installation at any job site.
            </p><br />
            <p class="text-sm md:text-base font-thin">
              Prepared for the installation of cameras, digital log systems, or
              real-time office connection, according to customer requirements.
            </p><br />
            <p class="text-sm md:text-base font-thin">
              Our control system is designed to be operated by a single person,
              reducing labor costs and simplifying plant operation.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div
    class="w-full max-w-7xl my-10 mx-auto px-8 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6"
  >
    <div>
      <Image src={img10} alt="Triaso workers operating the control cabin" class="rounded-md" />
    </div>
    <div class="justify-center flex flex-col">
      <h1
        class="font-bold text-center lg:text-end md:text-end text-black text-xl md:text-2xl"
      >
        MANUAL OPERATION
      </h1>
      <br />
      <p
        class="font-thin text-base text-center lg:text-justify md:text-justify md:text-lg"
      >
        We understand the importance of full operational control. That’s why our
        system includes a complete manual operation mode. We don’t depend on a
        fully automated setup—if a component stops working, the plant can
        continue running manually without interrupting production
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <OSection />

  <div
    class="w-full flex flex-col items-center justify-start text-black bg-[url(/HeroIntegral.webp)] bg-no-repeat bg-center bg-cover min-h-[550px] md:min-h-[700px]"
  >
    <div class="w-full max-w-7xl mx-auto px-8 my-4 md:my-14">
      <h1 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl text-start mb-1 md:mb-5 w-full font-bold">
        Integral 10 Tph <br /> Asphalt Plants
      </h1>
      <h2
        class="text-lg md:text-xl text-start w-full font-semibold text-[#393939]"
      >
        Ideal for municipal jobs and road maintenance
      </h2>
      <p class="mt-1 md:mt-5 text-[#313131] text-base md:text-lg font-thin">
        Full-Scale Technology in a Compact Format
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="pt-10">
    <h2 class="text-center font-bold text-black text-xl md:text-4xl">
      Everything in a single unit
    </h2>
  </div>
  <SlidersCarrusel client:load images={images2} />
  <div class="py-5 px-8 w-full text-center">
    <h2 class="text-center font-bold text-blueMain text-xl md:text-3xl">
      Sell at a lower price, attract more customers, and achieve higher profits
    </h2><br />
    <a href="/IntegralAphaltPlant" class="font-semibold text-blue-700 hover:text-blue-600 underline text-sm md:text-base text-center"
      >Learn more about our 10 TPH asphalt plants >
    </a>
  </div>
</div>
